{"tid":303783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天一度出現市政局百周年公園　大批警員戒備","createTime":"2017-06-30T12:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T13:43:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7a1cf6475608211c5eaf61347ead1f5b300af5","tid":303783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"原先計劃在尖沙咀鐘樓舉行集會的香港民族黨召集人陳浩天，在尖東東海商業中心外準備登上的士，一度被警員截停，警員向他發出口頭警告，指他如果舉行集會，屬非法行為，其後陳浩天再次登上的士離開。<br />\n<br />\n民族黨Facebook專頁指原定在尖沙咀鐘樓舉行的集會，改為尖東市政局百周年紀念公園附近舉行，陳浩天傍晚前，在公園一帶遊走，大批警員在場戒備。"},{"pid":"26db95ea342295b3ff1c369c3058e941d546e678","tid":303783,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1339271-20170630.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1339271-20170630.htm&d=Kfcaz5XCad%2BQwKRNpnvvq54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4f3bbba1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1339271-20170630.htm&h=fdde8e8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1339271-20170630.htm</a>"},{"pid":"97f07f920fd0b801b59eae2912736ebec297d9cd","tid":303783,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af03945dfded1a8687296d5ef103607cc9509c8","tid":303783,"uid":42820,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oriO9pNzCDE4PexnG/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oriO9pNzCDE4PexnG%2Fsource.gif&h=17808e72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74d9ccb62715828732a4ddbee53973c6985bf814","tid":303783,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/b